description: Motilal Oswal Midcap 100 ETF is an exchange traded fund launched by Motilal Oswal Securities Limited. It is managed by Motilal Oswal Asset Management Company Limited. The fund invests in the public equity markets of India. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in the stocks of mid-cap companies. It seeks to replicate the performance of the CNX Midcap Index, by investing in the stocks of companies as per their weightings in the index. Motilal Oswal Midcap 100 ETF was formed on January 12, 2011 and is domiciled in India.
name: Motilal Oswal Nifty Midcap 100 ETF
